	<div class="container promo-text">
		<div class="inner clearfix">
			<div class="col-md-11 col-sm-11 col-xs-12 no-padding">
				<h1>Trick or treat? Beware so a ransomware won’t end up between your Halloween sweets</h1>
<div class="excerpt">Ghosts, monsters and the living dead can all send a chill down one's spine. Ransomware, for some people, is just as spooky. This Halloween, we look at why.</div>
<div class="post-meta">
    <div class="wls-authors">
                <div class="wls-author with-avatar">
                            <div class="wls-author-avatar">
                    <a href="https://www.welivesecurity.com/author/okubovic/" title="Ondrej Kubovič">
                        <img src="https://www.welivesecurity.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/ondrej.kubovic@eset.skCB_-222x179.jpg" alt="Ondrej Kubovič">
                    </a>
                </div>
                        <div class="wls-author-name">
                <a href="https://www.welivesecurity.com/author/okubovic/" title="Ondrej Kubovič">
                    Ondrej Kubovič                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
            </div>
    <span class="meta">
		<span class="strong">
			<time datetime="2015-10-30 12:44:53">30 Oct 2015 - 12:44PM</time>
		</span>
			</span>
</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>	

            <div class="content">
                <div class="social-wrapper" id="social-sharer">
                    <span class="text">Share</span>
	<a class="share-facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.welivesecurity.com%2F2015%2F10%2F30%2Ftrick-or-treat-beware-so-a-ransomware-wont-end-up-between-your-halloween-sweets%2F" target="blank" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" data-original-title="Share on Facebook">
		<span class="icomoon icon-icon_fb"></span>
	</a>
	<a class="share-twitter" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.welivesecurity.com%2F2015%2F10%2F30%2Ftrick-or-treat-beware-so-a-ransomware-wont-end-up-between-your-halloween-sweets%2F&text=Trick or treat? Beware so a ransomware won’t end up between your Halloween sweets%0A&via=welivesecurity" target="blank" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" data-original-title="Share on Twitter">
		<span class="icomoon icon-icon_tw"></span>
	</a>
	<a class="share-linkedin" href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.welivesecurity.com%2F2015%2F10%2F30%2Ftrick-or-treat-beware-so-a-ransomware-wont-end-up-between-your-halloween-sweets%2F" target="blank" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" data-original-title="Share on Linkedin">
		<span class="icomoon icon-icon_in"></span>
	</a>
